Change Log for update to WRF 3DVAR code
---------------------------------------

Author: Dale Barker
Reviewer: Syed Rizvi
Date: 04/13/05

Reason for changes (explain before making changes)
--------------------------------------------------

Update gen_be code to work with latest wrfvar

Added additional bin_type options (still recommend
1 for global, and 5 for regional).

Expected Differences
--------------------

The gen_be code did not work for global as it hadn't
been updated for a while.

No changes to calculation of gen_be statistics are
expected.

Size of gen_be output file (used in 3D-Var) changes
slightly, hence change to backgroud error read routine.

CPU:

Same.

memory:

Same.

Test results (run on which machines?)
------------------------------------------------------

Spectral tests pass (test_spectral=.true.).

Regression coefficients, eigenvectors, eigenvalues, and 
power spectra plotted and compared with previous
standalone code.

